    <text>
        <body>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="cww.01102.002.jpg"/>
            <div1 type="petition" subtype="handwritten">  
                    <div2 type="section" subtype="handwritten"><opener>
                        <salute>To <choice><abbr>Hon.</abbr><expan>Honorable</expan></choice> Commissioners of Emancipation</salute>
                    </opener>
                    
                    <p><persName>John Brown</persName> Your Petitioner represents that he was the Slave of <persName>Richard Pettit</persName> of <placeName>Georgetown Dist of Columbia</placeName> That he is a free man under the act of Congress passed <date when="1862-04-16">April 16th 1862</date> that the said <persName>Robert Pettit</persName> have never filed a Petition under the late act of Congress Claiming Compensation from the <placeName>United States</placeName>, Your Petitioner prays that a Certificate of his Freedom may be granted to him by requesting the Clerk of the Circuit Court to grant him his freedom paper and as in duty bound will every pray</p>
                        <closer><signed><persName>R P Jackson</persName> <choice><abbr>Atty</abbr><expan>Attorney</expan></choice> for Petitioner</signed>
                    <dateline><date when="1862-08-12">August 12th 1862</date></dateline>
                            
                        </closer>  
                    </div2>
                <div2 type="section" subtype="handwritten"><ab>JGS 589</ab></div2>                  
            </div1>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="cww.01102.001.jpg"/>
            <div1 type="cover" subtype="handwritten">
                <ab>paid</ab>
                <ab><persName>John Brown</persName></ab>
                <ab>Schedule</ab>
                <ab>Amended Act.</ab>
                <ab>Filed <date when="1862-08-12">Aug 12th 1862</date></ab>
            </div1>            
        </body>
